# Platform boot-progress log captured by BMC (POST codes + UEFI stage messages)
POST 0x02 SEC: CPU early init OK
POST 0x15 SEC: microcode load OK
POST 0x32 PEI: memory init OK (24 DIMMs trained)
POST 0x4F PEI: DXE IPL handoff
POST 0x61 DXE: driver dispatch start
POST 0x9A DXE: PCI bus enumeration start
POST 0x9C DXE: PCI resource allocation complete
POST 0xB4 DXE: option ROM init complete (all devices)
POST 0xA0 BDS: boot device selection
POST 0xAD OS: OS loader handoff
